        <a href="https://med.stanford.edu/news/all-news/2016/10/withholding-amino-acid-depletes-blood-stem-cells.html">Withholding amino acid depletes blood stem cells</a>
        
        <p class="teaser">A new study shows that a diet deficient in valine effectively depleted the blood stem cells in mice and made it possible to perform a blood stem cell transplantation on them.</p>
    
